1-.download pakage http://sourceforge.net/projects/sdl2gfx/
2-.unpak
3-. sudo ./configure
4-. make
5-. sudo make install
6-. The libs (.so) files are installed in /usr/local/lib. Better.... copy all to  /usr/lib/i386-gnu-linux 
7.- copy all (.h) files from our dowloaded package to /usr/include/SDL2
8.- Be sure vapi files belongs in vapi directory: /usr/share/vala-0.20/vapi

for build your application:

valac -o "%e" --pkg sdl2 --pkg sdl2-gfx --pkg sdl2-ttf --pkg sdl2-image --pkg sdl2-mixer -X -lSDL2_image  -X -lSDL2_ttf -X -lSDL2_mixer -X -lSDL2_gfx "%f"
